### Arabic

فَكَذَّبُوهُ فَأَخَذَتْهُمُ ٱلرَّجْفَةُ فَأَصْبَحُوا۟ فِى دَارِهِمْ جَـٰثِمِينَ

### English

But they rejected him, so an ˹overwhelming˺ earthquake struck them and they fell lifeless in their homes.